<item>
            <title>[CXF-7639] Support Servlet 4.0 API in OSGI manifest</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-7639</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Our OSGI application cannot be deployed on top of tomcat 9, because tomcat 9 exposes javax.servlet.xxx packages in V 4.0, and various bundles from cxf who depends of javax.servlet exclude 4.0 from their osgi manifest.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems Servlet 4.0 is already supported, so the simple fix for this only seems to include servlet 4.0 in range of supported version (&#160;**&#160;[0,4.1) instead of [0,4.0) in Import-Package)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
